OL,3,CStreeting poised to launch leadership
OL,4,Cbid as Starmer clings on as PM
OL,6,FStreeting's team have not denied
OL,7,Fclaims he is poised to quit, while
OL,8,FLabour's trade union backers pulled
OL,9,Ftheir support for Starmer on Wednesday.
OL,11,FSo far, 87 MPs have publicly called
OL,12,Ffor Starmer's resignation, but they
OL,13,Fare not united behind a single
OL,14,Fcandidate to replace him.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
