OL,3,CStreeting poised to launch leadership
OL,4,Cbid as Starmer clings on as PM
OL,6,FIf he mounts a challenge, Streeting
OL,7,Fwill need the support of 81 Labour MPs
OL,8,Fto begin a formal contest.
OL,10,FOther potential challengers include
OL,11,Fformer deputy prime minister Angela
OL,12,FRayner, Energy Secretary and former
OL,13,Fparty leader Ed Miliband, Mayor of
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Andy Burnham, and
OL,15,Farmed forces minister Al Carns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
