OL,3,CStreeting poised to launch leadership
OL,4,Cbid as Starmer clings on as PM
OL,6,FBurnham would need an MP to step down
OL,7,Fin order for him to return to
OL,8,Fparliament, with Manchester
OL,9,Frepresentatives Afzal Khan and Jeff
OL,10,FSmith both rumoured in Westminster to
OL,11,Fbe willing to make way for him.
OL,13,FRayner told ITV News she had been
OL,14,Fcleared by HMRC of deliberate
OL,15,Fwrongdoing or carelessness over her
OL,16,Ftax affairs, potentially paving the
OL,17,Fway for her return to frontline
OL,18,Fpolitics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
