OL,3,CStreeting poised to launch leadership
OL,4,Cbid as Starmer clings on as PM
OL,6,FThe senior Labour MP stepped down in
OL,7,FSeptember when an independent ethics
OL,8,Fadvisor found she had broken
OL,9,Fministerial code after admitting she
OL,10,Fhad underpaid stamp duty on an
OL,11,F#800,000 flat in Hove, which was
OL,12,Fconsidered to be her second home.
OL,14,FAn HMRC investigation cleared her of
OL,15,Fany wrongdoing, concluding Rayner had
OL,16,Fnot sought to avoid paying the correct
OL,17,Fstamp duty and had since corrected it.
OL,19,FRayner told ITV News: "I've never
OL,20,Fwanted to avoid paying my tax.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
