PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778785872
OL,3,CStreeting poised to launch leadership
OL,4,Cbid as Starmer clings on as PM
OL,6,F"For me, that was the most distressing
OL,7,Fthing, that people felt that I was tax
OL,8,Fdodging or trying to set up trusts to
OL,9,Favoid tax, or being careless by not
OL,10,Ftaking the appropriate advice. And
OL,11,FHMRC has concluded that that isn't the
OL,12,Fcase."
OL,14,FEarlier this week, Rayner called on
OL,15,FStarmer to "set out the change our
OL,16,Fcountry needs" as she warned Labour is
OL,17,Ffacing its "last chance" after a
OL,18,Fdisastrous set of election results.
