OL,3,CStreeting poised to launch leadership
OL,4,Cbid as Starmer clings on as PM
OL,6,FStreeting and the PM sat down for
OL,7,Fcrunch talks in No 10 earlier on
OL,8,FWednesday, which lasted just 16
OL,9,Fminutes.
OL,11,FIn response to reports of a leadership
OL,12,Fchallenge by Streeting, a spokesman
OL,13,Ffor Starmer said he had "full
OL,14,Fconfidence" in the health secretary.
OL,16,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said Labour
OL,17,FMPs had an "important decision to
OL,18,Fmake" as she spoke to reporters
OL,19,Foutside Downing Street on Thursday
OL,20,Fmorning.
